{
  "video_id": "tvos4nORf_Y",
  "title": "How Will You Measure Your Life? Clay Christensen at TEDxBoston",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Denise RQ Reviewer: Lena Clemente"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10894.0,
      "end_time": 12595.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14146.0,
      "end_time": 19506.0,
      "text": "The world is, in many ways, organized in a nested system."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20165.0,
      "end_time": 22640.0,
      "text": "And so we have nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22505.0,
      "end_time": 24302.0,
      "text": "within those we have industries;"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24304.0,
      "end_time": 26717.0,
      "text": "within industries we have corporations;"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27395.0,
      "end_time": 29835.0,
      "text": "within those we have business units;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30850.0,
      "end_time": 32855.0,
      "text": "within those we have teams;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33405.0,
      "end_time": 35515.0,
      "text": "within the teams we have people;"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36650.0,
      "end_time": 38443.0,
      "text": "and within people we have our brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39415.0,
      "end_time": 40947.0,
      "text": "We are nested."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41706.0,
      "end_time": 43640.0,
      "text": "It turns out that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43650.0,
      "end_time": 49977.0,
      "text": "as I have and my colleagues have tried to understand how business works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51840.0,
      "end_time": 53537.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve developed a set of theories."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53974.0,
      "end_time": 58750.0,
      "text": "And when I say a theory, what I mean is a statement of causality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59107.0,
      "end_time": 63316.0,
      "text": "an understanding of what causes what and why."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63892.0,
      "end_time": 68467.0,
      "text": "Some of you know some of the theories. Disruption is a theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69157.0,
      "end_time": 75307.0,
      "text": "What it asserts is that the mechanism that causes successful companies to fall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75858.0,
      "end_time": 80867.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not that they&#39;re not at their work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81140.0,
      "end_time": 85170.0,
      "text": "but rather somebody comes in at the bottom of the market and moves up."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85728.0,
      "end_time": 90327.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that the mechanism, the pursue of profit from at the bottom of the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 91138.0,
      "end_time": 94127.0,
      "text": "that makes success so hard to sustain."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94486.0,
      "end_time": 96189.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s another theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96190.0,
      "end_time": 102200.0,
      "text": "called the theory of the preservation of modularity."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 103700.0,
      "end_time": 108648.0,
      "text": "The theory of the preservation of modularity"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 109790.0,
      "end_time": 113949.0,
      "text": "explains among the other things why the euro doesn&#39;t work"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114559.0,
      "end_time": 119610.0,
      "text": "and why SAP implementation systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 119990.0,
      "end_time": 126520.0,
      "text": "are so difficult and complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 126920.0,
      "end_time": 132179.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s another theory called jobs-to-be-done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 132929.0,
      "end_time": 137200.0,
      "text": "and what it asserts is that, you know, here&#39;s Clay;"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 137991.0,
      "end_time": 142829.0,
      "text": "I have characteristics: I&#39;m unfortunately 60 years old now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 143210.0,
      "end_time": 145929.0,
      "text": "I live in the suburbs, five children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 145930.0,
      "end_time": 151240.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, have all left and are living independently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 151241.0,
      "end_time": 154160.0,
      "text": "and life has become boring."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 154161.0,
      "end_time": 156280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 156281.0,
      "end_time": 159769.0,
      "text": "But the fact that I have those characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 159770.0,
      "end_time": 163731.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t cause me to go out and buy The New York Times."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 164836.0,
      "end_time": 167855.0,
      "text": "There might be a correlation between my characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 167856.0,
      "end_time": 170665.0,
      "text": "and the propensity to buy The New York Times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 170666.0,
      "end_time": 174892.0,
      "text": "but the characteristics don&#39;t cause me to do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 175510.0,
      "end_time": 177500.0,
      "text": "What causes us to do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 177501.0,
      "end_time": 183361.0,
      "text": "is there&#39;s a job that arises in our life and we have to get the job done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 183722.0,
      "end_time": 186662.0,
      "text": "and what causes us to buy a product or service"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 186663.0,
      "end_time": 188691.0,
      "text": "is we have to reach out and find something"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 188692.0,
      "end_time": 192231.0,
      "text": "that can do the job and pull it into our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 192542.0,
      "end_time": 195963.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the causal mechanism behind a purchase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 195964.0,
      "end_time": 199614.0,
      "text": "is understanding what&#39;s the job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 199615.0,
      "end_time": 204383.0,
      "text": "and the insight there is that the customer is the wrong unit of analysis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 204384.0,
      "end_time": 207000.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the job that we need to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 207200.0,
      "end_time": 209271.0,
      "text": "So these are all theories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 209272.0,
      "end_time": 214183.0,
      "text": "and some of you know those, and a number of others from our research."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 215223.0,
      "end_time": 219943.0,
      "text": "What we have learned, and inadvertently in many ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 219944.0,
      "end_time": 222655.0,
      "text": "is that these statements of causality"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 223224.0,
      "end_time": 227573.0,
      "text": "apply at every stage in this nested system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 228164.0,
      "end_time": 230753.0,
      "text": "and so, the theories help us understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 230754.0,
      "end_time": 234964.0,
      "text": "why nations lose their competitiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 235274.0,
      "end_time": 241640.0,
      "text": "why Japan was so successful and then died, for example;"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 241594.0,
      "end_time": 247165.0,
      "text": "and why America finds it so hard to regain our momentum;"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 247715.0,
      "end_time": 251135.0,
      "text": "- and that goes all the way down to the point of teams -"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 251944.0,
      "end_time": 257414.0,
      "text": "a number of years ago, in my course at the Harvard Business School."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 257664.0,
      "end_time": 260753.0,
      "text": "In this course, we study these theories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 260755.0,
      "end_time": 262304.0,
      "text": "try to understand them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 262305.0,
      "end_time": 264925.0,
      "text": "then put these theories on a set of lenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 264926.0,
      "end_time": 271736.0,
      "text": "and examine companies, or economies, or industries"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 272166.0,
      "end_time": 273545.0,
      "text": "and try to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 273546.0,
      "end_time": 277774.0,
      "text": "can we understand why things are happening the way they are happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 277775.0,
      "end_time": 281926.0,
      "text": "and what actions would lead to what results."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 282626.0,
      "end_time": 284936.0,
      "text": "At the end of the course, on the last day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 284937.0,
      "end_time": 286697.0,
      "text": "rather than asking them"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 286977.0,
      "end_time": 291387.0,
      "text": "to just put on these lenses and examine yet another company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 292127.0,
      "end_time": 294396.0,
      "text": "I asked them to look in the mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 294811.0,
      "end_time": 296327.0,
      "text": "and ask them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 296717.0,
      "end_time": 302587.0,
      "text": "\"Can you explain why your life is the way it is today"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 302973.0,
      "end_time": 305200.0,
      "text": "because of these theories?\","
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 305490.0,
      "end_time": 309616.0,
      "text": "and \"Can you predict what will happen in your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 309617.0,
      "end_time": 313560.0,
      "text": "if you continue to do what you are now doing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 313208.0,
      "end_time": 315545.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s been a remarkable experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 315546.0,
      "end_time": 320375.0,
      "text": "to see the students come back on the last day of class"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 320376.0,
      "end_time": 325467.0,
      "text": "and with causal theories as the explanation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 325948.0,
      "end_time": 328486.0,
      "text": "what they need to change in their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 328488.0,
      "end_time": 334198.0,
      "text": "so that their life will be the life that they hoped to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 334668.0,
      "end_time": 337137.0,
      "text": "And I thought, I just offer a couple of these"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 337138.0,
      "end_time": 341691.0,
      "text": "in the hopes that as entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 341717.0,
      "end_time": 344662.0,
      "text": "and ambitious people"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 345268.0,
      "end_time": 348820.0,
      "text": "you end up living the life that you hope you will live."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 349998.0,
      "end_time": 352798.0,
      "text": "So one of the things we observed, as I mentioned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 352799.0,
      "end_time": 356548.0,
      "text": "is that what kills successful companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 356549.0,
      "end_time": 359688.0,
      "text": "is somebody comes in at the bottom of the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 359689.0,
      "end_time": 363528.0,
      "text": "So if you go back a few years ago in telecommunications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 363529.0,
      "end_time": 367217.0,
      "text": "the Darwins of the industry were Lucent and Nortel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 367940.0,
      "end_time": 370678.0,
      "text": "made circuit switching technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 370838.0,
      "end_time": 374777.0,
      "text": "and this rusty, little or small company"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 374778.0,
      "end_time": 379824.0,
      "text": "not very consequential called Cisco emerged."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 380868.0,
      "end_time": 384770.0,
      "text": "And their technology, the router, wasn&#39;t good enough to be used in voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 385197.0,
      "end_time": 388659.0,
      "text": "but they deployed it at the bottom of the market with data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 388660.0,
      "end_time": 393551.0,
      "text": "and then went up market, and ultimately, killed Lucent and Nortel."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 394270.0,
      "end_time": 398849.0,
      "text": "The reason why is that when they look down at the router,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 398851.0,
      "end_time": 402230.0,
      "text": "the router on every dimension wasn&#39;t as good."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 402231.0,
      "end_time": 405182.0,
      "text": "So they kept making better and better"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 408162.0,
      "end_time": 409952.0,
      "text": "circuit switch devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 410812.0,
      "end_time": 413271.0,
      "text": "And we ask ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 413272.0,
      "end_time": 416695.0,
      "text": "\"I wonder who decided at Lucent"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 416696.0,
      "end_time": 419750.0,
      "text": "that they should go out and get killed?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 419760.0,
      "end_time": 420825.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 420826.0,
      "end_time": 425160.0,
      "text": "\"And when was the date on which they decided they would get killed?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 425161.0,
      "end_time": 428390.0,
      "text": "And the answer, of course, is that nobody made the decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 428400.0,
      "end_time": 431191.0,
      "text": "In fact, what happened is all the individual people"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 431192.0,
      "end_time": 435172.0,
      "text": "in a very successful organization did everything right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 435372.0,
      "end_time": 438520.0,
      "text": "but because they did all of these things independently"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 438521.0,
      "end_time": 441802.0,
      "text": "and what made sense in those circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 441803.0,
      "end_time": 445983.0,
      "text": "when it summed up, it summed up to disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 446793.0,
      "end_time": 451354.0,
      "text": "The reason why it sums up to disaster"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 451904.0,
      "end_time": 456204.0,
      "text": "is they&#39;re trying to maximize their profitability"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 456414.0,
      "end_time": 459924.0,
      "text": "and typically, the way you calculate profitability:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 460433.0,
      "end_time": 463591.0,
      "text": "tomorrow&#39;s investments that pay off tomorrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 464431.0,
      "end_time": 465820.0,
      "text": "go to the bottom line"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 465821.0,
      "end_time": 469779.0,
      "text": "and are much more tangible than investment that pay off ten years from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 470704.0,
      "end_time": 475743.0,
      "text": "When I go back to my graduating classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 475744.0,
      "end_time": 481597.0,
      "text": "I graduated from the MBA program at Harvard in 1979,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 482217.0,
      "end_time": 484977.0,
      "text": "we have a reunion every five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 485987.0,
      "end_time": 490345.0,
      "text": "When we came back for a fifth reunion, man, everybody was happy;"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 490775.0,
      "end_time": 492994.0,
      "text": "most of our classmates had married"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 492995.0,
      "end_time": 496404.0,
      "text": "people who are much better looking than my classmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 496405.0,
      "end_time": 497534.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 497535.0,
      "end_time": 499584.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re doing well in their career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 499585.0,
      "end_time": 504222.0,
      "text": "but as we hit the tenth, the 15th, 20th, and then the 25th anniversaries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 504656.0,
      "end_time": 507944.0,
      "text": "oh my gosh, my friends were coming back"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 508674.0,
      "end_time": 511342.0,
      "text": "not happy with their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 511344.0,
      "end_time": 514543.0,
      "text": "And very many of them have gotten divorced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 514544.0,
      "end_time": 517875.0,
      "text": "and their spouses had remarried, and they were raising"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 517876.0,
      "end_time": 521875.0,
      "text": "their - my classmates&#39; - children on the other side of the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 521876.0,
      "end_time": 523885.0,
      "text": "alienated from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 523885.0,
      "end_time": 527574.0,
      "text": "I guarantee that none of my classmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 527575.0,
      "end_time": 530964.0,
      "text": "ever planned when they graduated from the business school"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 530965.0,
      "end_time": 533134.0,
      "text": "to go out, and get divorced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 533135.0,
      "end_time": 535775.0,
      "text": "and have children who hate their guts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 535776.0,
      "end_time": 538356.0,
      "text": "and are being raised by other [parents],"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 538746.0,
      "end_time": 542215.0,
      "text": "and yet, a very large portion of our my classmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 542216.0,
      "end_time": 544295.0,
      "text": "actually implemented a strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 544296.0,
      "end_time": 546625.0,
      "text": "that they never planned to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 546626.0,
      "end_time": 548204.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 548206.0,
      "end_time": 550576.0,
      "text": "It turns out that the reason why they do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 550577.0,
      "end_time": 555797.0,
      "text": "is the very same mechanism and that is that pursuit of achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 556327.0,
      "end_time": 561670.0,
      "text": "So, we all, everybody here, is driven to achieve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 561707.0,
      "end_time": 566746.0,
      "text": "and when you have an extra ounce of energy or 30 minutes of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 566747.0,
      "end_time": 569786.0,
      "text": "instinctively and unconsciously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 569787.0,
      "end_time": 573536.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll allocate it to whatever activities in your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 573537.0,
      "end_time": 577447.0,
      "text": "give you the most immediate evidence of achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 577767.0,
      "end_time": 582416.0,
      "text": "And our careers provide that immediate evidence of achievement:"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 582417.0,
      "end_time": 585186.0,
      "text": "we closed a sale, we ship a product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 585187.0,
      "end_time": 587106.0,
      "text": "we finish a mid-presentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 587107.0,
      "end_time": 592390.0,
      "text": "we close a deal, we get promoted, we get paid."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 592759.0,
      "end_time": 597850.0,
      "text": "Our careers provide the most, very tangible, immediate achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 598667.0,
      "end_time": 600279.0,
      "text": "In contrast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 600819.0,
      "end_time": 605779.0,
      "text": "investments in our families don&#39;t pay off for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 606139.0,
      "end_time": 608780.0,
      "text": "In fact, on a day-to-day basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 608790.0,
      "end_time": 611519.0,
      "text": "our children misbehave over and over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 611789.0,
      "end_time": 616670.0,
      "text": "and it really it isn&#39;t until 20 years down the road you can look at your children"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 616671.0,
      "end_time": 620429.0,
      "text": "and be able to put your hands on your hips and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 620430.0,
      "end_time": 622878.0,
      "text": "\"We raised great children.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 622880.0,
      "end_time": 628869.0,
      "text": "But on a day-to-day basis, achievement isn&#39;t at hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 628870.0,
      "end_time": 630969.0,
      "text": "when we invest in relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 630970.0,
      "end_time": 635290.0,
      "text": "with our family, their children, and our spouses."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 635300.0,
      "end_time": 640680.0,
      "text": "And as a consequence, people like you and I who plan to have a happy life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 640681.0,
      "end_time": 643621.0,
      "text": "because our families truly are"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 643622.0,
      "end_time": 647261.0,
      "text": "the deepest source of happiness in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 647262.0,
      "end_time": 649510.0,
      "text": "find that although that&#39;s what we want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 649511.0,
      "end_time": 653820.0,
      "text": "the way we invest our time, and energy, and talents"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 654290.0,
      "end_time": 659261.0,
      "text": "causes us to implement a strategy that we wouldn&#39;t at all plan to pursue."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 660232.0,
      "end_time": 662800.0,
      "text": "And so I wanted to just offer that one;"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 663131.0,
      "end_time": 665531.0,
      "text": "is something to think about."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 666112.0,
      "end_time": 670161.0,
      "text": "The reason why successful companies fail"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 670642.0,
      "end_time": 673622.0,
      "text": "is they invest in things that provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 673623.0,
      "end_time": 677712.0,
      "text": "the most immediate and tangible evidence of achievement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 677713.0,
      "end_time": 681671.0,
      "text": "and the reason why they have such a short time horizon"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 681673.0,
      "end_time": 685722.0,
      "text": "is that they are run by people like you and I."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 685723.0,
      "end_time": 690781.0,
      "text": "We then apply that very same thinking process"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 690783.0,
      "end_time": 694843.0,
      "text": "in our personal lives with sad results."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 695933.0,
      "end_time": 701203.0,
      "text": "Let me just offer another thought that might be useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 703725.0,
      "end_time": 707945.0,
      "text": "I was driving to work a number of years ago early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 708965.0,
      "end_time": 713115.0,
      "text": "and when I was on Huron Avenue in Cambridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 713525.0,
      "end_time": 715275.0,
      "text": "I just had a feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 716105.0,
      "end_time": 720624.0,
      "text": "that something important was going to happen to Clay Christensen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 720625.0,
      "end_time": 722466.0,
      "text": "that I was going to be given"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 722467.0,
      "end_time": 727446.0,
      "text": "a much more consequential business opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 727447.0,
      "end_time": 730447.0,
      "text": "than I have just as a plain, old professor."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 730687.0,
      "end_time": 733933.0,
      "text": "A couple of weeks later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 733934.0,
      "end_time": 737363.0,
      "text": "somebody who was in that position announced that he was leaving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 737364.0,
      "end_time": 739975.0,
      "text": "and I put two and two together and decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 740605.0,
      "end_time": 743295.0,
      "text": "\"Gosh! Sounds like, for whatever reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 743296.0,
      "end_time": 748116.0,
      "text": "I just had this feeling that I&#39;m going to be his replacement.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 749226.0,
      "end_time": 753476.0,
      "text": "So the day came, and they chose another person."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 753916.0,
      "end_time": 757755.0,
      "text": "I wondered why did I have that feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 757756.0,
      "end_time": 760956.0,
      "text": "that an important thing was going to happen to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 761286.0,
      "end_time": 765156.0,
      "text": "Did the people kind of lose guts? Or... I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 765897.0,
      "end_time": 769588.0,
      "text": "But I wrestled with"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 770958.0,
      "end_time": 774237.0,
      "text": "how will they measure Clay Christensen&#39;s life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 774238.0,
      "end_time": 780176.0,
      "text": "If they&#39;re going to not make me the leader of a large institution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 781486.0,
      "end_time": 784936.0,
      "text": "how do I know whether my life has been worth living?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 784937.0,
      "end_time": 787638.0,
      "text": "And again, how I measure my life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 788345.0,
      "end_time": 793867.0,
      "text": "I realized that I studied this for a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 794627.0,
      "end_time": 796987.0,
      "text": "and I reached the strangest conclusion:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 797637.0,
      "end_time": 804560.0,
      "text": "that God doesn&#39;t employ accountants or statisticians."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 805188.0,
      "end_time": 811936.0,
      "text": "And what I mean by that is, because you and I have finite minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 812356.0,
      "end_time": 816269.0,
      "text": "when we try to understand what&#39;s going on in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 816543.0,
      "end_time": 819222.0,
      "text": "we have to aggregate things."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 819223.0,
      "end_time": 820748.0,
      "text": "So in your companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 820750.0,
      "end_time": 824249.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t keep track of every individual invoice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 824250.0,
      "end_time": 827180.0,
      "text": "and so you have to aggregate all those up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 827190.0,
      "end_time": 830190.0,
      "text": "so that you have receivables, and payables, and revenues."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 830919.0,
      "end_time": 834328.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t keep track of every element of cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 834329.0,
      "end_time": 838737.0,
      "text": "and so you have to aggregate all that up into total cost categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 838738.0,
      "end_time": 842905.0,
      "text": "and then you subtract that from this, and there&#39;s a number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 842906.0,
      "end_time": 848104.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the way we try to understand the world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 848106.0,
      "end_time": 852255.0,
      "text": "is because we have limited minds, we have to aggregate things up."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 852256.0,
      "end_time": 856420.0,
      "text": "And then we&#39;ll look at that number compared to last year&#39;s number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 856701.0,
      "end_time": 859910.0,
      "text": "and if it&#39;s better, then we say we&#39;re doing better."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 859911.0,
      "end_time": 865502.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the way we look at the world because of our but minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 866500.0,
      "end_time": 869300.0,
      "text": "It has then another interesting effect on us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 869310.0,
      "end_time": 872400.0,
      "text": "and that is, because we have to aggregate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 872420.0,
      "end_time": 875822.0,
      "text": "we get a sense of hierarchy in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 876310.0,
      "end_time": 877597.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 878101.0,
      "end_time": 884650.0,
      "text": "people who are higher up in larger organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 884651.0,
      "end_time": 886271.0,
      "text": "are more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 886273.0,
      "end_time": 889490.0,
      "text": "than people who preside"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 889500.0,
      "end_time": 892399.0,
      "text": "over fewer numbers of people and fewer numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 892400.0,
      "end_time": 894682.0,
      "text": "down the road, down the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 894683.0,
      "end_time": 897441.0,
      "text": "So we tend to this, we get this sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 897442.0,
      "end_time": 902222.0,
      "text": "that people who achieve in a hierarchical sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 902432.0,
      "end_time": 907115.0,
      "text": "their lives will be judged somehow as better"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 907715.0,
      "end_time": 911475.0,
      "text": "having lived than those below."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 911851.0,
      "end_time": 915392.0,
      "text": "We measure sometimes how high we go or how successful we are"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 915393.0,
      "end_time": 918122.0,
      "text": "by how much money we make."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 918123.0,
      "end_time": 923511.0,
      "text": "But these are all the result of our having limited minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 923512.0,
      "end_time": 927551.0,
      "text": "and their having to aggregate measures of success."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 930313.0,
      "end_time": 933333.0,
      "text": "This choice of measurement"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 933334.0,
      "end_time": 936333.0,
      "text": "is actually a big deal;"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 936334.0,
      "end_time": 939334.0,
      "text": "in a company, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 939532.0,
      "end_time": 945258.0,
      "text": "if you measure profitability by return on net assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 946188.0,
      "end_time": 948127.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 948128.0,
      "end_time": 950489.0,
      "text": "and sure, you could be innovative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 950490.0,
      "end_time": 953617.0,
      "text": "develop successful, new products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 953618.0,
      "end_time": 958668.0,
      "text": "and take that profitability and stick it into the numerator of the ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 958948.0,
      "end_time": 962563.0,
      "text": "but you can also reduce the denominator of the ratio"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 962564.0,
      "end_time": 964943.0,
      "text": "by outsourcing everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 964944.0,
      "end_time": 966795.0,
      "text": "and the ratio doesn&#39;t matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 966796.0,
      "end_time": 970405.0,
      "text": "whether you build it from the top or subtract from the bottom;"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 970406.0,
      "end_time": 974897.0,
      "text": "if profitability is measured by return on net assets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 974899.0,
      "end_time": 978898.0,
      "text": "it causes us to manage it in a particular way."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 978899.0,
      "end_time": 980830.0,
      "text": "And in a similar way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 980831.0,
      "end_time": 984670.0,
      "text": "if we follow our professor&#39;s advices from finance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 984671.0,
      "end_time": 988181.0,
      "text": "and we measure profitability on innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 988182.0,
      "end_time": 992111.0,
      "text": "in terms of internal rate of return or IRR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 992112.0,
      "end_time": 993510.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a ratio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 993511.0,
      "end_time": 999630.0,
      "text": "and sure, you could get the ratio up by being successful with innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 999631.0,
      "end_time": 1003160.0,
      "text": "but you also could get that measure up"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1003160.0,
      "end_time": 1007299.0,
      "text": "by only investing in short-term projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 1007310.0,
      "end_time": 1012690.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s just the long way of saying, be careful in how you measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 1014250.0,
      "end_time": 1016849.0,
      "text": "profitability in your company."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 1016850.0,
      "end_time": 1019548.0,
      "text": "So how do you measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 1020670.0,
      "end_time": 1022996.0,
      "text": "the success of your life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 1023000.0,
      "end_time": 1026378.0,
      "text": "As I mentioned, it&#39;s because we have to aggregate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 1026380.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1030620.0000000001,
      "text": "we have this sense of hierarchy, wealth, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1031000.0,
      "end_time": 1036423.0,
      "text": "But the reason I concluded that God doesn&#39;t employ accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1036960.0,
      "end_time": 1039749.0,
      "text": "is he has an infinite mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1039750.0,
      "end_time": 1042837.0,
      "text": "and what that means is he doesn&#39;t have to aggregate up"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1042839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1045839.9999999999,
      "text": "above the level of individual people"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1046630.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1052920.0,
      "text": "in order to have a perfect understanding of what&#39;s going on in this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1053780.0,
      "end_time": 1055879.0,
      "text": "When I realized that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1055880.0,
      "end_time": 1061899.0,
      "text": "that he doesn&#39;t have to aggregate up above the level of individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1061900.0,
      "end_time": 1064420.0,
      "text": "then I realized, \"Oh, my goodness!"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1065250.0,
      "end_time": 1069681.0,
      "text": "When I have my interview with God at the end of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1069690.0,
      "end_time": 1072408.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s not going to show me"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1072410.0,
      "end_time": 1077429.0,
      "text": "how high I went into anybody&#39;s org-chart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1077430.0,
      "end_time": 1081629.0,
      "text": "or how much money I left behind in the bank when I died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1081630.0,
      "end_time": 1087380.0,
      "text": "but rather he&#39;s going to say, &#39;Oh, Clay, I put you in that circumstance."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1087390.0,
      "end_time": 1089941.0,
      "text": "Now, can we talk about the individual people"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1089940.0,
      "end_time": 1093379.0,
      "text": "whose lives you help to become better people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1093380.0,
      "end_time": 1097207.0,
      "text": "because you worked with them, or they were members of your family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1097210.0,
      "end_time": 1101590.0,
      "text": "or you just met them, and they needed your help."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1101600.0,
      "end_time": 1103720.0,
      "text": "And then Clay, I stuck you in this situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1103720.0,
      "end_time": 1109499.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about the individual people whose lives you blessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1109500.0,
      "end_time": 1113261.0,
      "text": "because you use the talents I gave you to help them.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1113410.0,
      "end_time": 1117112.0,
      "text": "And I realized that that&#39;s the way God will measure my life;"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1117110.0,
      "end_time": 1121302.0,
      "text": "is the individual people whose lives I blessed."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1122720.0,
      "end_time": 1126341.0,
      "text": "I just want to offer that as the second takeaway"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1126340.0,
      "end_time": 1131117.0,
      "text": "from at least, what Clay Christensen is thinking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1131130.0,
      "end_time": 1133502.0,
      "text": "and that is it&#39;s actually really important"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1133500.0,
      "end_time": 1136758.0,
      "text": "that you succeed at what you&#39;re succeeding at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1136760.0,
      "end_time": 1140239.0,
      "text": "but that isn&#39;t going to be the measure of your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1140240.0,
      "end_time": 1144461.0,
      "text": "God doesn&#39;t count, he doesn&#39;t aggregate;"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1145470.0,
      "end_time": 1147652.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s just going to assess you"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1147650.0,
      "end_time": 1152769.0,
      "text": "on the basis of how well you helped other people be better people."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1152770.0,
      "end_time": 1154617.0,
      "text": "Well, God bless you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1154630.0,
      "end_time": 1157830.0,
      "text": "I hope that some of these ideas will be helpful to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1157840.0,
      "end_time": 1159255.0,
      "text": "and that you all will be successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1159260.0,
      "end_time": 1162510.0,
      "text": "in the way that God will measure success."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1162870.0,
      "end_time": 1164754.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1164760.0,
      "end_time": 1165446.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}